{"tid":87953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最新蕭析：曾俊華參選 葉劉哭了 北京力挺林鄭還是最後DQ林鄭？","createTime":"2017-01-20T08:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T08:50:05.000Z","uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8dfa3673964abef5f0e13ba4f957d2f87a5923","tid":87953,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:30:08.000Z","msg":"近日有關特首選舉的現象，每每都在顯示林鄭是被中央欽點之人。田北俊踢爆有非中聯辦的有地位人士向他遊說，大家會估到一那個人應是董建華，於是大家便會想到，為何陳智思會轉軚幫林鄭。當日董建華重用陳智思，因此他要還董建華人情，而這，又顯示董建華在熱烈地干預香港政治&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n - See more at: <a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/17331#sthash.wR8v1QAo.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F17331%23sthash.wR8v1QAo.dpuf&d=IT0WKWL4evWOYlI9S0Ou9GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=469c4400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/17331#sthash.wR8v1QAo.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"858d2f522edbd4767fd9f3ce8ec79c5ea8012c8a","tid":87953,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:31:38.000Z","msg":"Burnhill the Prophet<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb42fabc38d510621fde82c24439dd16e6b3616","tid":87953,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T08:50:05.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅嘅crying in the party？"}]}